info_json.title: AAI Industry

info_json.title: Adjustable Magazine Size
info_json.author: SnipSnipSnipered
info_json.description: This mod allows you to adjust the amount of ammo in most magazine-type items. Natively compatible with modded ammunitions using Factorio's 'ammo-category' system.

info_json.title: Copper construction robots
info_json.author: Genhis
info_json.description: Early-game construction robots. They are quite slow and have limited reach, but they get the job done.

info_json.name: HeroTurretRedux
info_json.title: HeroTurrets_Redux
info_json.author: ForTheKing55
info_json.description: Turrets are built using salvaged self-learning AI tech from your ship allowing them to get deadlier with practice.  Extends turrets via ranking system based on kills. Turrets generated so not limited to vanilla, identifiable by overlaid rank insignia. Rank buffs individual turrets.
